trans-unit.source: Represents an ARGB (alpha, red, green, blue) color.
trans-unit.target: (알파, 빨간색, 녹색, 파랑) ARGB 색을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Named colors are represented by using the properties of the Color structure.
trans-unit.target: 명명 된 색은 색 구조체의 속성을 사용 하 여 표현 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about these colors, see [Colors by Name](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=92332).
trans-unit.target: 이러한 색에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 [색 이름](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=92332)합니다.

trans-unit.source: The color of each pixel is represented as a 32-bit number: 8 bits each for alpha, red, green, and blue (ARGB).
trans-unit.target: 각 픽셀의 색은 32 비트 숫자도 표시 됩니다: 각각 알파, 빨간색, 녹색 및 파랑 (ARGB)에 8 비트입니다.

trans-unit.source: Each of the four components is a number from 0 through 255, with 0 representing no intensity and 255 representing full intensity.
trans-unit.target: 네 개의 구성 요소가 0부터 농도가 없음을 나타내고 255 전체 강도 나타내는 0부터 255 까지의 숫자입니다.

trans-unit.source: The alpha component specifies the transparency of the color: 0 is fully transparent, and 255 is fully opaque.
trans-unit.target: 알파 구성 요소는 색상의 투명도 지정 합니다.: 0은 완전히 투명 하며, 255은 완전히 불투명 합니다.

trans-unit.source: To determine the alpha, red, green, or blue component of a color, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Color.A%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Color.R%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Color.G%2A>, or <xref:System.Drawing.Color.B%2A> property, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 알파, 색의 빨강, 녹색 또는 파란색 구성 요소를 확인 하려면 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Drawing.Color.A%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Color.R%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Color.G%2A>, 또는 <xref:System.Drawing.Color.B%2A>속성을 각각.</xref:System.Drawing.Color.B%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Color.G%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Color.R%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Color.A%2A>

trans-unit.target: 사용자 지정 색 중 하나를 사용 하 여 만들 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Drawing.Color.FromArgb%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Drawing.Color.FromArgb%2A>

trans-unit.source: The alpha component specifies the transparency of the color: 0 is fully transparent, and 255 is fully opaque.

trans-unit.source: A predefined color is also called a known color and is represented by an element of the <xref:System.Drawing.KnownColor> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 미리 정의 된 색은 색을 알려진된 라고도 하며의 요소에서 나타내는 <xref:System.Drawing.KnownColor>열거형.</xref:System.Drawing.KnownColor>

trans-unit.source: When the ToString method is applied to a <xref:System.Drawing.Color> structure that is created by using the <xref:System.Drawing.Color.FromArgb%2A> method, ToString returns a string that consists of the ARGB component names and their values, even if the ARGB value matches the ARGB value of a predefined color.
trans-unit.target: ToString 메서드에 적용 된 경우는 <xref:System.Drawing.Color>사용 하 여 만든 구조는 <xref:System.Drawing.Color.FromArgb%2A>메서드, ToString 문자열을 반환 ARGB 구성 요소 이름과 해당 값으로 구성 된 미리 정의 된 색의 ARGB 값과 일치 하는 경우에.</xref:System.Drawing.Color.FromArgb%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Color>

trans-unit.source: A string that is the name of this <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref>, if the <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> is created from a predefined color by using either the <xref:System.Drawing.Color.FromName*> method or the <xref:System.Drawing.Color.FromKnownColor*> method; otherwise, a string that consists of the ARGB component names and their values.
